title: Lindsay Arnold From Dancing With The Stars!
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew chat with Lindsay Arnold from Dancing With The Stars! She tells us about how it felt to be in the public eye at such a young age, talks her most embarrassing moment on the show and her plans to balance motherhood with her career!
